dc_title_s: Delaware River Harbor Lines: Pennsylvania Shore from mouth of Schuykill River to Greenwich Point, New Jersey Shore from Red Bank to Newton Creek
dc_description_s: Map shows the area along the Delaware River from Red Bank to Newton Creek in New Jersey and the Schuykill River to Greenwich Point in Pennsylvania. |Map shows parts of League Island, Howell Cove, Big Timber Creek, Schuylkill River, Horse Shoe Shoal, and Newton Creek. Map also has detailed sketches showing locations of stations and a table of course, bearings, and distances
